items.desc: Welcome to the Xionic Madness Wiki, the main source of information for Xionic Madness! This growing wiki is the definite source of information for Xionico's Madness Series, Xionic Madness. Enter the wiki to find information on the entertaining series, its various characters, and helpful tips. Contributors are welcome!
